_sText:
Two areas seperated by walls, each with 6 spawn points for HE's & 2 spawn point for Smokes.  Start off with 1 HE grenade & the knife.  Can boost ppl over the wall for knife fights.  After about 90 seconds tunnel opens.  After 150 seconds, health of all players will start to drop by 5hp every 5 secs.  

Size: 1569KB
Type: HE & Knife
Spawns: 32 each for t's and ct's - 64 Total (Not recommended tho)
